public static class FhirXdTransaction.Transaction extends org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.DocumentManifest
The class Transaction is a derived FHIR resource containing all information about destination and submission-set including documents for a transaction (e.g. IHE XDS submission or IHE XDM portable media creation)
